| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0441 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: edc5d90b-5fe0-5f0c-825c-7a9991d9fda1"
